# This is a placeholder certificate file
#
# To enable HTTPS support:
# 1. Start the hub with TLS enabled in blentinel_hub.toml
# 2. The hub will generate hub_tls_cert.pem on first run
# 3. Copy hub_tls_cert.pem to this file (probe/hub_cert.pem)
# 4. Rebuild the probe
#
# Until you complete these steps, the probe will only work with HTTP URLs.
